snippet.title: Toggle Tile Steam Demo
snippet.description:
My new puzzle game has a playable demo on Steam now.
Toggle all the tiles to solve the puzzle.

Demo store page:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3165730/Toggle_Tile_Demo/
